                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9600" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1443</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1499 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智升阶，“药”焕新：人机协同下重药集团财务数智化转型之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Smart Steps, New Drugs: The Journey of Financial Digital Intelligence Transformation of C.Q. Pharmaceutical Holding Co., Ltd. under Human-Machine Collaboration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨兴龙，蒋彩环，王春寒，李明逸，邱天，周琨荻，黄雅伦，芦凌波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆医药（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务数智化；人机协同；平衡计分卡；员工画像</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Human-computer collaboration; financial digital intelligence; balanced scorecard; dynamic theory; organizational inertia theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例详细阐述了重药集团在数字化浪潮中，通过财务数智化转型提升企业运营效率，进而推动高质量发展的实践。通过建立财务共享中心，重药集团形成了战略财务、共享财务和业务财务为核心的财务三角色体系。然而，随着企业规模扩大和业务量增加，共享中心面临系统瓶颈，如校验规则延迟、业财系统不兼容及财务人员适应性问题。为此，重药集团启动财务数智化2.0，优化系统并赋能业务，同时运用平衡计分卡和员工画像技术重塑人才结构，帮助员工从财务会计向管理会计的转型。在人机协同过程中，重药集团深刻认识到人的核心地位，坚持“以人为本”的理念。本案例旨在引导学生理解，在宏观环境变迁中，医药企业如何运用开放性和权变策略推动战略革新，构建竞争优势，并克服转型挑战，实现人与技术的高效协同，推动高质量发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case details C.Q. Pharmaceutical Holding Co., Ltd.&#39;s practice of improving the operational efficiency of the enterprise through the transformation of financial digital intelligence in the wave of digitization, and then promoting high-quality development. Through the establishment of a financial sharing center, C.Q. Pharmaceutical Holding Co., Ltd. has formed a three-role system of finance centered on strategic finance, shared finance and business finance. However, with the expansion of the enterprise scale and the increase of business volume, the shared center faces system bottlenecks, such as the delay of the calibration rules, the incompatibility of the business finance system and the adaptability of financial personnel. For this reason, C.Q. Pharmaceutical Holding Co., Ltd. has launched Finance Numerical Intelligence 2.0 to optimize the system and empower the business, and at the same time, it has used the balanced scorecard and employee portrait technology to reshape the talent structure and help employees transform from financial accounting to management accounting. In the process of human-machine collaboration, C.Q. Pharmaceutical Holding Co., Ltd. deeply recognizes the core position of human beings and adheres to the concept of “people-oriented”. This case aims to guide students to understand how pharmaceutical companies can use openness and contingency strategies to promote strategic innovation, build competitive advantages, overcome transformation challenges, and realize the efficient synergy between people and technology to promote high-quality development in a changing macro-environment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》、《财务数智化等课程》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务数智化；人机协同；平衡计分卡；数据画像；动态理论；组织惯性理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
